{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1783433127121,"sessionID":"ses_0c31ab9f9ffeQ78106pyBoIj54","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"mk-spec-memory_memory_match_triggers","callID":"call_0x4LGD8yhvN34O5463Z8F0dO","state":{"status":"error","input":{"prompt":"You are orchestrating the deep-review workflow YAML as a detached fan-out lineage.\nThis is an explicit parallel-detached OpenCode lineage, not a self-invocation of the parent session.\nUse the separate lineage directory and session id below as the detached state boundary.\n\n\nRead .opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/deep-review/SKILL.md and execute the review loop with these parameters:\n  spec_folder: .opencode/specs/system-skill-advisor/000-migration-from-system-speckit\n  config.fanout_lineage_artifact_dir: /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-skill-advisor/000-migration-from-system-speckit/review/lineages/gpt-2\n  session_id: fanout-gpt-2-1783433085887-cah79b\n  executor: cli-opencode model=openai/gpt-5.5-fast\n  loop_type: review\n  config.stopPolicy: max-iterations\n  config.maxIterations: 20\n  config.convergenceThreshold: 0.1\n\nReview setup bindings (emit before any writes, same as native PRE-BOUND SETUP ANSWERS):\nreview_target: .opencode/specs/system-skill-advisor/000-migration-from-system-speckit\nreview_target_type: spec-folder\nreview_dimensions: all\nspec_folder: .opencode/specs/system-skill-advisor/000-migration-from-system-speckit\nexecution_mode: AUTONOMOUS\nlineage_mode: auto\n\nThe step_resolve_artifact_root step will bind artifact_dir to /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-skill-advisor/000-migration-from-system-speckit/review/lineages/gpt-2 via the\nconfig.fanout_lineage_artifact_dir override — do NOT run the resolveArtifactRoot node\ncommand; bind artifact_dir directly to the override value.\n\nRun phase_init, phase_main_loop (until config.maxIterations is reached; treat convergence before that as telemetry only and broaden review angles instead of synthesizing early), and phase_synthesis.\nWrite all outputs to /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-skill-advisor/000-migration-from-system-speckit/review/lineages/gpt-2. Do not touch any path outside /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-skill-advisor/000-migration-from-system-speckit/review/lineages/gpt-2.\n\nWhen complete, output a single line: FANOUT_LINEAGE_COMPLETE:gpt-2","specFolder":".opencode/specs/system-skill-advisor/000-migration-from-system-speckit","tenantId":"","userId":"","agentId":"","limit":5,"session_id":"fanout-gpt-2-1783433085887-cah79b","turnNumber":1,"include_cognitive":true},"error":"{\n  \"summary\": \"Error: sessionId \\\"fanout-gpt-2-1783433085887-cah79b\\\" does not match a server-managed session. Omit sessionId to start a new server-generated session and reuse the effectiveSessionId returned by the server.\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"error\": \"sessionId \\\"fanout-gpt-2-1783433085887-cah79b\\\" does not match a server-managed session. Omit sessionId to start a new server-generated session and reuse the effectiveSessionId returned by the server.\",\n    \"code\": \"E_SESSION_SCOPE\",\n    \"details\": {\n      \"requestedSessionId\": \"fanout-gpt-2-1783433085887-cah79b\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"hints\": [\n    \"Omit session_id to start a new server-generated session, or reuse the effectiveSessionId returned by memory_context.\"\n  ],\n  \"meta\": {\n    \"tool\": \"memory_match_triggers\",\n    \"tokenCount\": 223,\n    \"cacheHit\": false,\n    \"isError\": true,\n    \"severity\": \"error\",\n    \"tokenBudget\": 3500\n  }\n}","time":{"start":1783433119675,"end":1783433127119}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_0be4bdfbce4d1331016a4d079392f08190a4c35490820ab409"}},"id":"prt_f3ce598a700125WMof8Q8i1VQL","sessionID":"ses_0c31ab9f9ffeQ78106pyBoIj54","messageID":"msg_f3ce5494400142M3q4PURIqkMh"