{"type":"text","timestamp":1783433281569,"sessionID":"ses_0c31ab9f9ffeQ78106pyBoIj54","part":{"id":"prt_f3ce820a90011meGckNwKcwtVS","messageID":"msg_f3ce804c4001gRDFXfe74QNaan","sessionID":"ses_0c31ab9f9ffeQ78106pyBoIj54","type":"text","text":"The packet’s current docs claim the migration is complete with known accepted validator debt and deferred memory indexing. I’m verifying those claims against the filesystem, metadata, and validation commands before recording findings.","time":{"start":1783433273513,"end":1783433281564},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0c71e1cb2c041477016a4d08397d9c81918d45f3acd3ce9bbd","phase":"commentary"}}}}
